    "description": "我们可爱的亚洲主题 DLC 为您带来了专属宠物、室内装饰品和建筑外观，让自己置身于度假氛围之中，享受远东的异国风情！<br><br><strong>新宠物</strong> <br>一位非常特别的客人从亚洲远道而来参观您的农场：一只超级可爱的小松鼠想成为您的新朋友！与最可爱的小伙伴一起享受所有即将到来的冒险。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695660/extras/5e3f5b3d17518944099007efa0c3bd2c.poster.avif?t=1655279812\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695660/extras/5e3f5b3d17518944099007efa0c3bd2c.webm?t=1655279812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695660/extras/5e3f5b3d17518944099007efa0c3bd2c.mp4?t=1655279812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>室内装饰</strong> <br>为您的农场房屋寻找最美的亚洲主题家具和装饰。获得一张舒适的新床、一个可爱的休息区、令人惊叹的新窗户和地板设计以及异国情调的新装饰品，如植物、镜子和图片。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695660/extras/acee7d89fe8d9779b316524e00516984.poster.avif?t=1655279812\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695660/extras/acee7d89fe8d9779b316524e00516984.webm?t=1655279812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695660/extras/acee7d89fe8d9779b316524e00516984.mp4?t=1655279812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><strong>建筑皮肤 </strong><br>从内到外都很漂亮。采用独特的亚洲主题设计改造您的农场房屋、磨坊和风车！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695660/extras/22d83bf1c7bd327bf4469be124aea15f.poster.avif?t=1655279812\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695660/extras/22d83bf1c7bd327bf4469be124aea1